  - Rebalance timeout expiration handler (GroupCoordinatorShard: timeout callback)
  - Member fencing logic (lines 4189-4206: consumerGroupFenceMember/consumerGroupFenceMembers)
  - Metadata update group refresh (lines 5955-5960: requestMetadataRefresh for affected groups)
